title: Game Pack 3 - Casino Games (Fake Money) (December 11 2013)
description:
Both of these games do not uses real money. You can not win real money. Both do have scoreboards.

(LastEnd Casino Slots)
Try your luck at slot machines in this 3D environment. Casino Slots has Random Number Generators which are continually generating so the game play is always changing. This is a nice way to try out your luck on slot machines without using real money. Casino Slots features an online high scoreboard that allow you to compare your luck and skill against other players from around the world.

(LastEnd Blackjack)
LastEnd Blackjack features an online high scoreboard that allow you to compare your skills against other players from around the world. 

"Includes game engine"
